WEBVTT

00:08.792 --> 00:10.166
[upbeat music]

00:10.208 --> 00:12.709
- Uh, hey, guys,

00:10.208 --> 00:12.709
I got our sleeping bags.

00:12.750 --> 00:13.959
Little help?

00:14.834 --> 00:16.291
- Yes!

00:24.083 --> 00:26.750
Oh, you're done, perfect.

00:26.792 --> 00:29.542
Now we can practice for our

00:26.792 --> 00:29.542
sleepover at the history museum.

00:29.583 --> 00:31.083
- Practice sleeping?

00:31.125 --> 00:33.917
I can do that

00:31.125 --> 00:33.917
with my eyes closed.

00:35.458 --> 00:38.208
- No, practice not sleeping.

00:38.250 --> 00:40.667
This is finally our year

00:38.250 --> 00:40.667
to go on the big class trip,

00:40.709 --> 00:42.667
and something epic

00:40.709 --> 00:42.667
always happens,

00:42.709 --> 00:44.333
and if it happens

00:42.709 --> 00:44.333
in the middle of the night,

00:44.375 --> 00:46.709
I want to be awake so I can say,

00:46.750 --> 00:48.667
"I was there when..."

00:48.709 --> 00:50.875
- When what?

00:48.709 --> 00:50.875
- It's a saying.

00:50.917 --> 00:54.250
- That says what?

00:50.917 --> 00:54.250
- That says we saw the epic

00:50.917 --> 00:54.250
moment that became the stuff of

00:50.917 --> 00:54.250
legend.

00:54.291 --> 00:56.000
- When?

00:56.041 --> 00:58.375
- It hasn't happened yet.

00:56.041 --> 00:58.375
- Then how did we see it?

00:58.417 --> 01:00.417
- We didn't,

00:58.417 --> 01:00.417
but we're hoping to be there

01:00.458 --> 01:02.333
when it happens.

01:00.458 --> 01:02.333
- When what happens?

01:02.375 --> 01:04.750
together: The epic moment!

01:04.792 --> 01:06.875
- Like the year Nate Powell

01:04.792 --> 01:06.875
got his pajamas stuck

01:06.917 --> 01:08.250
on the saber tooth tiger--

01:08.291 --> 01:12.375
oh, and pantsed himself

01:08.291 --> 01:12.375
in front of everyone.

01:12.417 --> 01:14.125
- Hey, I wonder

01:12.417 --> 01:14.125
what's gonna happen this year.

01:14.166 --> 01:16.250
- Oscar's always

01:14.166 --> 01:16.250
sticking his head in stuff.

01:16.291 --> 01:18.667
Maybe he'll get it stuck

01:16.291 --> 01:18.667
in something at the museum.

01:18.709 --> 01:22.291
- Now why would you go

01:18.709 --> 01:22.291
and stick your head in that?

01:22.333 --> 01:23.792
- I just wanted

01:22.333 --> 01:23.792
to see if it would fit.

01:23.834 --> 01:26.792
[all laugh]

01:26.834 --> 01:28.959
- That would be epic,

01:29.000 --> 01:31.917
but nobody really

01:29.000 --> 01:31.917
gets their head caught in stuff.

01:31.959 --> 01:33.166
- Uh, guys?

01:36.709 --> 01:37.917
Dicky.

01:37.959 --> 01:39.625
- I just wanted

01:37.959 --> 01:39.625
to see if it would fit.

01:41.500 --> 01:43.208
- Turn your head the other way.

01:45.834 --> 01:47.542
- Whoa.

01:49.500 --> 01:52.291
- Well, time to not

01:49.500 --> 01:52.291
get to sleep.

01:52.333 --> 01:54.792
- Dawn, we're just

01:52.333 --> 01:54.792
as excited as you are,

01:54.834 --> 01:57.667
but don't you think it's better

01:54.834 --> 01:57.667
to get as much rest as possible

01:57.709 --> 01:59.542
before we go?

01:57.709 --> 01:59.542
- He has a point.

01:59.583 --> 02:02.417
Shouldn't you be doing the exact

01:59.583 --> 02:02.417
opposite of what your plan is?

02:02.458 --> 02:05.875
- Even I see the value

02:02.458 --> 02:05.875
in a good night's sleep.

02:05.917 --> 02:07.834
- You play like you train,

02:07.875 --> 02:09.583
and you don't train

02:07.875 --> 02:09.583
for a marathon

02:09.625 --> 02:10.834
by sitting in a chair.

02:09.625 --> 02:10.834
- I would.

02:10.875 --> 02:13.208
- Sounds smart.

02:10.875 --> 02:13.208
- I'm training right now.

02:15.041 --> 02:17.041
- Fine, don't stay up,

02:17.083 --> 02:20.041
but if this epic moment happens

02:17.083 --> 02:20.041
while you guys are all asleep,

02:20.083 --> 02:21.625
I'm not waking you.

02:21.667 --> 02:23.583
- All right,

02:21.667 --> 02:23.583
we'll stay up all night.

02:23.625 --> 02:24.834
How hard could it be?

02:24.875 --> 02:26.875
[both snoring]

02:26.917 --> 02:28.542
- [grumbles]

02:28.583 --> 02:32.500
- It's only been five minutes,

02:28.583 --> 02:32.500
you wimps.

02:32.542 --> 02:35.834
<i>[upbeat music]</i>

02:35.875 --> 02:38.208
Well, well, well,

02:38.250 --> 02:40.834
looks like I was the only one

02:38.250 --> 02:40.834
to stay up last night.

02:40.875 --> 02:42.542
[sneezes]

02:40.875 --> 02:42.542
- Bless you.

02:42.583 --> 02:43.875
[boys chuckle]

02:43.917 --> 02:45.458
- What's so funny?

02:45.500 --> 02:47.041
- Just that you

02:45.500 --> 02:47.041
stayed up all night

02:47.083 --> 02:48.750
and got yourself sick.

02:47.083 --> 02:48.750
- And if you're sick,

02:48.792 --> 02:50.208
there's no way Mom and Dad

02:50.250 --> 02:52.000
will let you go on the trip.

02:52.041 --> 02:54.625
- Oh, please.

02:52.041 --> 02:54.625
I probably just caught a whiff

02:54.667 --> 02:55.875
of your body spray.

02:55.917 --> 02:57.458
- [sniffs]

02:57.500 --> 03:01.750
[groans]

02:57.500 --> 03:01.750
He is not wearing body spray.

03:01.792 --> 03:05.709
- Well, one sneeze

03:01.792 --> 03:05.709
doesn't mean I'm sick.

03:05.750 --> 03:07.583
[sneezing]

03:05.750 --> 03:07.583
- Bless you.

03:07.625 --> 03:09.250
Bless you...

03:07.625 --> 03:09.250
Bless you.

03:09.291 --> 03:10.792
- Bless you.

03:09.291 --> 03:10.792
- [sneezes]

03:10.834 --> 03:11.959
- Bless you.

03:14.000 --> 03:17.709
- Uh-oh.

03:14.000 --> 03:17.709
[boys laugh]

03:17.750 --> 03:19.542
<i>[upbeat music]</i>

