<i>♪ Na, na, na, na, na, na,</i>

03:22.208 --> 03:24.792
<i>na, na, na, na, na, ♪</i>

03:24.834 --> 03:27.792
<i>[whistling]</i>

03:27.834 --> 03:31.125
<i>♪ ♪</i>

03:31.166 --> 03:33.291
<i>- ♪ One, two, three, four! ♪</i>

