<i>- ♪ Na, na, na, na, na, na ♪</i>

03:42.750 --> 03:44.792
<i>♪ Na, na, na, na, na, na ♪</i>

03:42.750 --> 03:44.792
<i>- ♪ Hey! ♪</i>

